http://localhost:8080/ffcssomfz

O.	start_j2ee是本人学习j2ee的项目源代码集合.除了官方的代码示例外,还参考了一些网上论坛博客的资源.
本项目采用maven3.涉及到的技术有:struts2,lucene3,quartz1,spring3,hibernate3.6...以及各个框架之间的整合,
比如struts2+lucene,spring+quartz[+lucene]
ssj:struts,sprign,jpa
ssh:struts,spring,hibernate
ssi:struts,spring,ibatis
ssm:struts,spring,mybatis
smm:spring,spingMVC,mybatis
-------------------------------------------------------------------框架版本
概览:
	struts2
	lucene3
	quartz1
	spring3:
	jpa2:(ssj)
		hibernate-entitymanager =>JPA的实现
	hibernate3.6:(ssh)
		hibernate-entitymanager	=>必须滴
		hibernate-core			=>包含了annotations and commons-annotations

问题:
struts2和spring集成,使用spring2.5版本.如果Spring要使用3.0+?
 采用exclusions.见pom.xml中关于struts2的配置

struts2和hibernate3都依赖slf4j javassist.如果两者依赖的版本不一样?

候选版本:
javassist
	3.8.0.GA
	3.12.0.GA
Spring:
	3.0.5.RELEASE
	3.1.0.RELEASE
Hibernate:
	3.3.1.GA
	3.5.6-Final
	3.6.1.Final
	3.6.8.Final
	After Hibernate3.5,annotations and commons-annotations integration to hibernate-core
        <dependency>  
            <groupId>org.hibernate</groupId>  
            <artifactId>hibernate-commons-annotations</artifactId>  
            <version>3.2.0.Final</version>  
        </dependency>
       	<dependency>
			<groupId>org.hibernate</groupId>
			<artifactId>hibernate-annotations</artifactId>
			<version>3.5.6-Final</version>
		</dependency>
